AMEX,OPEN,Forum,is,a,community,of,business,owners,built,around,the,American,Express,card,OPEN,Forum,is,an,online,community,to,exchange,insights,get,advice,from,experts,and,build,connections,to,help,small,businesses,The,OPEN,Forum,API,allows,developers,to,build,applications,that,offer,functionality,such,as,the,ability,to,search,for,and,retrieve,details,about,the,most,recent,most,viewed,most,commented,and,most,shared,articles,and,videos,in,the,OPEN,Forum,archive,It,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML